name: enoyl-CoA hydratase
names: short chain enoyl coenzyme A hydratase
comment: Acts in the reverse direction. With cis-compounds, yields (3R)-3-hydroxyacyl-CoA. cf. EC 4.2.1.74 long-chain-enoyl-CoA hydratase.

orthologs.K01825: 3-hydroxyacyl-CoA dehydrogenase / enoyl-CoA hydratase / 3-hydroxybutyryl-CoA epimerase / enoyl-CoA isomerase
